<span class="math">$D_{J^c}(X) = -\\sum\\nolimits_{j \\in [m] \\backslash J} \\frac{z_I(X)\\mu_j(\\alpha)}{z_I(0)v_j(X - v_i^{-1})}</span>$</p>

